 * Allow multiple authoritative documents to upload
 * Create a set of demo documents that demonstrate how this works. For example: requirements for a private person buying a phone, against a specification or review of a single phone. 
 * Chaptered Source Structure: Organize the single HTML file into the 7 chapters (Header, Vendored Libs, Model Manager, State Engine, Core Logic, AI Pipeline, UI).
 * Model Sideloading (Chapter 3): Create the "Import" UI to allow users to select local model files and store them in IndexedDB (NOT localStorage).
 * Model Unloading/Eviction: Add a "Purge Models" button in Settings that wipes the IndexedDB object stores to prevent Ivanti MDM sync bloat.
 * Vanilla i18n: Implement a simple dictionary-based translation system for all UI strings (NL/EN).
